$幹部ドムドラ_歩行
$幹部ドムドラ_歩行
Darugnoa: "What do you want, Domudora?"
Darugnoa: "You must have a good reason to disturb my slumber."

Wisdom General Domudora: "My apologies. However, I thought it
necessary to report..."

Wisdom General Domudora: "Just now, Lord Galves was defeated by Pony-
Celes and has died in battle."

Wisdom General Domudora: "But as expected of Lord Galves. With his
last strength, he managed to take Pony-Celes with him in a self-
destruct."
Darugnoa: "..."
Darugnoa: "I see, you've done well to report this."
Wisdom General Domudora: "...?"
Wisdom General Domudora: "Is that all there is to say...?"
Darugnoa: "What are you trying to say?"

Wisdom General Domudora: "The greatest threat that you, Lord Darugnoa,
were concerned about has been eliminated. Yet your expression... what
does it mean?"
Darugnoa: "Did you think I would show a moment of weakness in relief?"
Wisdom General Domudora: "!?"

Darugnoa: "It's unlike you to bring your close aide Zaibog for an
audience."

Darugnoa: "Surely you're not thinking of taking this opportunity to
strike me down?"
Wisdom General Domudora: "Ugh!?"
Wisdom General Domudora: "No...! That's not it at all!"
Darugnoa: "You may come out now."
Wisdom General Domudora: "A combatant?"
Darugnoa: "Report to me once more."

Combatant: "During the battle with Pony-Celes in the Aban district,
Lord Galves died due to the treachery of Lord Domudora."

Combatant: "I was hiding and listening. I heard the final conversation
between Lord Galves and Lord Domudora."
Combatant: "There, Lord Domudora clearly stated..."

Combatant: "'In order to assassinate Lord Darugnoa, I must first
dispose of Lord Galves, who has been entrusted as his guard...'"

Wisdom General Domudora: "That's a lie, Lord Darugnoa! The words of a
mere combatant...!"
Darugnoa: "That may be so."
Darugnoa: "Show your face. You, who are called Samejima."
$鮫島拓実_歩行
$鮫島拓実_歩行
Wisdom General Domudora: "...!!"

Darugnoa: "This one has not yet undergone the transformation into a
combatant. He's just a human dressed in a combatant's uniform."
Wisdom General Domudora: "Then!"

Wisdom General Domudora: "All the more reason not to trust the words
of a human!"
Darugnoa: "Hahaha, do you not understand, even someone like you?"
Darugnoa: "This man risked his life to seek an audience with me."
Darugnoa: "Where would be the sense in him telling such lies?"

Darugnoa: "Besides, it's not common for mere humans to show such
remarkable courage, is it?"

Darugnoa: "Different species though we may be, this man could be
useful, don't you think?"
Wisdom General Domudora: "...Guh!"
Darugnoa: "You may step back now, Samejima."

Darugnoa: "Now, what will you do? Will you still bare your fangs at
me?"

Wisdom General Domudora: "Guh, not a single opening... This could
jeopardize the plan..."
Darugnoa: "Domudora."
Darugnoa: "I shall give you a chance."
Wisdom General Domudora: "What!?... You will spare my life...?"
Wisdom General Domudora: "I-I had planned to take you down..."
Darugnoa: "I have but one wish."
Darugnoa: "To completely eradicate Pony-Celes from this world."
Darugnoa: "If that is achieved, I shall let this rebellion slide."

Wisdom General Domudora: "But Pony-Celes should already be gone from
this world..."
Darugnoa: "Pony-Celes is not yet dead."

Darugnoa: "Perhaps it's the influence of nearing full revival... I can
tell. The balance between light and darkness is still maintained..."
Wisdom General Domudora: "..."
Wisdom General Domudora: "If you say so, then I understand."

Wisdom General Domudora: "I will find Pony-Celes and, risking my life,
I will surely—!"
Darugnoa: "I am counting on you, Domudora."
Darugnoa: "Do not disappoint me again."
Wisdom General Domudora: "Ha ha!"
